    CR -->|full CRUD| SchedulerPG
    CR -->|full CRUD| NetPol
    CR -->|create, list, update, watch| Roles
    CR -->|create, list, update, watch| RoleBindings
    CR -->|get, list, update, watch| VWC

    %% Namespace-scoped Role Permissions
    R -->|get, list, watch| Secrets

